<% content_for :title, "Cookies Policy | Afida" %>

<% content_for :meta_description, "Learn how Afida uses cookies and similar technologies on our website, what they do, and how you can manage them in your browser." %>

<div class="bg-gray-50 min-h-screen">
  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="bg-white border-b">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 max-w-4xl">
      <h1 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl text-gray-900 mb-3">Cookies Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600">Effective Date: 6th November 2025</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8 max-w-4xl">
    <!-- Introduction Card -->
    <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 lg:p-8 mb-8 shadow-sm">
      <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
        This Cookies Policy explains how B&B Eco, Ltd ("we," "our," or "the Company") uses cookies and similar tracking technologies on afida.com. It should be read alongside our <%= link_to "Privacy Policy", privacy_policy_path, class: "text-primary hover:underline" %>, which describes how we handle personal data more generally.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mt-4">
        Questions? Contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@afida.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">hello@afida.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Quick Navigation -->
    <nav class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8 shadow-sm">
      <h2 class="text-sm text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wide mb-4">Contents</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-sm">
        <a href="#what-are-cookies" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-primary">1. What Are Cookies</a>
        <a href="#how-we-use" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-primary">2. How We Use Cookies</a>
        <a href="#types" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-primary">3. Types of Cookies We Use</a>
        <a href="#third-party" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-primary">4. Third-Party Cookies</a>
        <a href="#manage" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-primary">5. Managing Cookies</a>
        <a href="#consent" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-primary">6. Your Consent</a>
        <a href="#updates" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-primary">7. Policy Updates</a>
        <a href="#contact" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-primary">8. Contact</a>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
      <!-- Section 1 -->
      <section id="what-are-cookies" class="p-6 lg:p-8 border-b border-gray-100">
        <h2 class="text-xl text-gray-900 mb-4">1. What Are Cookies</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Cookies are small text files placed on your device (computer, tablet, or phone) when you visit a website. They allow the site to recognise your device on subsequent visits and to store information about your preferences and activity.</p>
        <p class="text-gray-600">We also use related technologies such as web beacons, pixels, and local storage. For brevity, we refer to all of these as "cookies" in this policy.</p>
      </section>

      <!-- Section 2 -->
      <section id="how-we-use" class="p-6 lg:p-8 border-b border-gray-100">
        <h2 class="text-xl text-gray-900 mb-4">2. How We Use Cookies</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">We use cookies to:</p>
        <ul class="text-gray-600 text-sm space-y-2 ml-4">
          <li>• Keep you signed in and remember items in your cart</li>
          <li>• Process secure checkouts and payments</li>
          <li>• Remember your preferences, such as recently viewed products</li>
          <li>• Understand how visitors use the site so we can improve it</li>
          <li>• Measure the performance of our marketing</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <!-- Section 3 -->
      <section id="types" class="p-6 lg:p-8 border-b border-gray-100">
        <h2 class="text-xl text-gray-900 mb-4">3. Types of Cookies We Use</h2>

        <div class="overflow-x-auto">
          <table class="w-full text-sm">
            <thead>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-200">
                <th class="text-left py-2 pr-4 text-gray-900">Type</th>
                <th class="text-left py-2 pr-4 text-gray-900">Purpose</th>
                <th class="text-left py-2 text-gray-900">Duration</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="text-gray-600">
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-100">
                <td class="py-2 pr-4 align-top">Strictly necessary</td>
                <td class="py-2 pr-4 align-top">Enable core functions such as signing in, cart, and checkout. The site cannot work without these.</td>
                <td class="py-2 align-top">Session and persistent</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-100">
                <td class="py-2 pr-4 align-top">Preference</td>
                <td class="py-2 pr-4 align-top">Remember choices you make, such as recently viewed products.</td>
                <td class="py-2 align-top">Persistent</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-100">
                <td class="py-2 pr-4 align-top">Analytics</td>
                <td class="py-2 pr-4 align-top">Help us understand how visitors interact with the site so we can improve it.</td>
                <td class="py-2 align-top">Persistent</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-2 pr-4 align-top">Marketing</td>
                <td class="py-2 pr-4 align-top">Measure the effectiveness of our advertising and marketing campaigns.</td>
                <td class="py-2 align-top">Persistent</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Section 4 -->
      <section id="third-party" class="p-6 lg:p-8 border-b border-gray-100">
        <h2 class="text-xl text-gray-900 mb-4">4. Third-Party Cookies</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Some cookies are set by third parties whose services we use to operate or improve the site. These currently include:</p>
        <ul class="text-gray-600 text-sm space-y-2 ml-4">
          <li>• Stripe, for processing payments securely</li>
          <li>• Google Analytics and Google Ads, for measuring traffic and the performance of marketing campaigns</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-4">These providers operate under their own privacy and cookie policies. We do not control the cookies they set.</p>
      </section>

      <!-- Section 5 -->
      <section id="manage" class="p-6 lg:p-8 border-b border-gray-100">
        <h2 class="text-xl text-gray-900 mb-4">5. Managing Cookies</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">You can control and manage cookies through your browser settings. Most browsers let you:</p>
        <ul class="text-gray-600 text-sm space-y-2 ml-4 mb-4">
          <li>• See what cookies are stored and delete them individually</li>
          <li>• Block third-party cookies</li>
          <li>• Block cookies from specific sites</li>
          <li>• Block all cookies</li>
          <li>• Delete all cookies when you close the browser</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Blocking strictly necessary cookies will affect how the site works. For example, you may not be able to sign in or complete a checkout.</p>
      </section>

      <!-- Section 6 -->
      <section id="consent" class="p-6 lg:p-8 border-b border-gray-100">
        <h2 class="text-xl text-gray-900 mb-4">6. Your Consent</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">By continuing to use our website, you consent to our use of cookies as described in this policy. Where required by law, we will ask for your consent before placing non-essential cookies on your device.</p>
      </section>

      <!-- Section 7 -->
      <section id="updates" class="p-6 lg:p-8 border-b border-gray-100">
        <h2 class="text-xl text-gray-900 mb-4">7. Policy Updates</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">We may update this Cookies Policy from time to time to reflect changes to the cookies we use or to comply with legal requirements. We will post any changes on this page with an updated effective date.</p>
      </section>

      <!-- Section 8 -->
      <section id="contact" class="p-6 lg:p-8 bg-gray-50 rounded-b-lg">
        <h2 class="text-xl text-gray-900 mb-3">8. Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2">If you have questions about our use of cookies, please contact us at:</p>
        <a href="mailto:hello@afida.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">hello@afida.com</a>
      </section>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer Note -->
    <p class="text-center text-sm text-gray-500 mt-8 pb-8">
      This Cookies Policy is effective as of the date listed above.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
